  "about": {
    "title": "The Voidstone Philosophy",
    "paragraph1": "Voidstone Studio is a sanctuary for the maximalist soul. We reject the transient nature of fast fashion in favor of slow, deliberate creation. Our pieces are handcrafted for those who view fashion not as a trend, but as a wearable art form—bold, layered, and unapologetically unique.",
    "paragraph2": "Since our founding in 2024, we have dedicated ourselves to sustainability and craftsmanship. By focusing on handcrafted techniques and thoughtful production, we ensure that every garment is not just an item of clothing, but a statement piece designed to last. We don't follow trends; we empower individuals to define their own.",
    "mission": "Our Manifesto",
    "missionText": "To champion individuality in a world of conformity. We believe that true style is abundant, expressive, and deeply personal. Through sustainable practices and maximalist design, we create handcrafted pieces that allow you to stand out, stay true to yourself, and wear your story with pride."
},
